(define/contract (minimum-cost nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  (define (is-palindrome? n)
    (equal? (number->string n) (list->string (reverse (string->list (number->string n))))))
  
  (define (find-closest-palindrome n)
    (let loop ((i 0))
      (cond
        ((is-palindrome? (+ n i)) (+ n i))
        ((is-palindrome? (- n i)) (- n i))
        (else (loop (+ i 1))))))
  
  (let* ((sorted-nums (sort nums <))
         (median (if (even? (length nums))
                     (/ (+ (list-ref sorted-nums (quotient (length nums) 2))
                           (list-ref sorted-nums (- (quotient (length nums) 2) 1)))
                        2)
                     (list-ref sorted-nums (quotient (length nums) 2))))
         (closest-palindrome (find-closest-palindrome median)))
    (foldl (lambda (num acc) (+ acc (abs (- num closest-palindrome)))) 0 nums)))
